Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家 之前说的东西带来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.62,0:00:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想你们应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剩下的时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暑假作业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要在一天之内全部解决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在暑假的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们应付着还没做完的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是早就做完了喔
