Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 数学作业的讲义居然有10页
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今年的数学作业布置太多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说 你每年都是留到最后一天写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说啊 一般的学生基本上都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正你又是第一天就全部做完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留到之后再做很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学写得怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我每天都会做一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以只剩一些就完成了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像藤宫同学这样的优等生 一点也不讨人厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是讨人厌的优等生还真对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我最担心的还是山岸同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喔 等好久了 锵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天打电话过去时 她连到底有什么作业也不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更准确的应该这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我忘记的是暑假要结束了这件事本身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你之前都是怎么解决暑假作业的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟人借来抄的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还真是一点也没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 山岸同学跟将吾是青梅竹马对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？你们小学不是一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}分在同一个班级？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一向只记得快乐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想起什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 有个想看的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那要去楼下看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐 香织也一起看嘛 很有趣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是作业还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都还没开始做的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以防万一先问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你没有生山岸同学的气吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这点小事不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看着山岸平常的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就知道她没有恶意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来你看得挺仔细的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然满口抱怨 你也还是经常为山岸同学操心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是喜欢照顾人的类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是对你就真的有点火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学 怎么样 有点进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不…完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有不会的地方 尽管问我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最不可或缺的还是可靠的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像你这样就特别需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大伙儿 我端了茶跟点心过来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思 东西乱成一堆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事 没事 是暑假作业对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在想如果一起做暑假作业的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是就能体验回到年轻时代的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 我今天还烤了蛋糕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待会下来吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你们慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学的妈妈真的很亲切呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你们就加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你多少客气一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也想睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山岸同学也来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来解决掉作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家一起努力的话很快就做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的只剩一点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我再自己努力一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说我是真不会做数学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学是不是想得太复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}数学是像谜题和游戏一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有着明确的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了寻找它而旅行 这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是解法有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以找出答案的时候才有强烈的成就感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有聪明的解法 也有自由的解法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有绕了远路也能一步步接近答案的解法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算不是漂亮的解法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要自己努力想出来的答案是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是会很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我认为解出来之前的过程才重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 说太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织真是喜欢数学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听过大家会来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一大早就做好等着大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饮料就红茶行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那能把这个拿到那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希 头顶的柜子里有茶叶罐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能拿一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:07:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我小学有过个子这么高的同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想以前不是这个身高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是香织小学时候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暑假的时候全家去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感觉就像回到了那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织每天都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说好想快点开学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在半年前这是无法想象的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那孩子竟能交到朋友 能如此绽开笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朋友的力量真是伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里 我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 难道是朋友以上的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:08:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开玩笑啦 开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还是想做香织的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每天都能吃到这么美味的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有今天才这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有很多 多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好吃了 多少我都吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剩下了可以带回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我给你续茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}桐生同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有帮到藤宫同学的忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学所面临的问题 我还完全没为她解决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 或许根本就不是可以解决的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过程才重要不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}借藤宫的话说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起问题的解决
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}解决之前的经历才更重要对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样的话 维持现状就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么什么 说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么 在说这个蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是从未品尝过的美味 真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么会 太夸张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我差不多该回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说了晚饭之前回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}作业自己做没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二学期开始之后距离交作业还有几天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}船到桥头自然直吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要帮家里人买东西 差不多该撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 将吾也走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有一张卷子就做完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那做完再回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就剩我们俩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我走那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}数学作业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}计算式和答案帮你写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么时候写的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才 闲着没事干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:12:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前好像也有人帮我做过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在鞋柜里 也有过一本笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}经常会想是谁为我做的呢 一直都是个迷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是桐生同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个时候的你 一直被人说迟钝什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管被别人说什么 你都不会尝试去解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是希望那本笔记能成为你改变自己的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是第一次受到别人的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我很想被这样值得信赖的人照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的做法错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 桐生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小学的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今往后我也一直期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}终于结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不懂的地方有藤宫同学教我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比一个人做更能集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有没有帮到长谷同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那还用说 我一直有受到藤宫同学的帮助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 要写进日记里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学很努力把作业都做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个夏天留下了好多回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多亏了长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这话该我说才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 话说回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么藤宫同学能大致记住我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 突然之间问奇怪的问题 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学自己能知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不用费力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自从和长谷同学相识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得自己的内心发生了改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前我已经放弃结交朋友的想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常害怕去结交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一想到记忆会消失 不可能一直做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然如此 那就干脆不要朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直都这么想着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自从和长谷同学相识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才了解到不管有什么隐情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有些朋友都会一直伴我左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要翻看日记 就能了解到长谷同学是怎样的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能够发自内心地信任一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心情变得十分轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}变得不再害怕结交新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也都是长谷同学的功劳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不介意的话 吃了晚饭再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去和妈妈说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 这怎么好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有没有撞到哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}灰尘 粘到头发上了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听到了好大动静 你们两个怎么…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才只是个小意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高中生正值精力旺盛的时期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在这方面还是很理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以说是误会啦 藤宫妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我懂的 我懂的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我绊了一下 然后藤宫同学就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在早上遇到还真难得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感觉今天会有什么好事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好事已经发生了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了调整心情 我们开始换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抽签决定 按顺序上来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要坐最后的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明几乎所有人都这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真亏你能光明正大地说出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那开始换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先去趟办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又不是盘算着提前吃便当 或者睡午觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种动机不纯的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坐在后面的话 就可以看到藤宫同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得动机已经足够不纯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看 果然有好事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呀 看起来真幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我后面是小蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来第二学期也可以平安度过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为她会帮我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 我听到了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蓝和我不一样 可严厉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好担心沙希啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂 别把人说的跟魔鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了 回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有件事要告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们来了个转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了 进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}女生 来吧来吧来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的假的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这位是从北海道搬来的九条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我叫九条一 请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随便找个空位置就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就最后排那个位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道你是藤宫香织？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哈？你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全不记得我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候你都没有遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是说我这个人根本无足轻重以至于被彻底忘记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学 藤宫同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚刚真是吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你突然倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是你能醒来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山岸同学也很担心你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾虽然嘴上没说 但也很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我上课也完全无法集中精力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 你叫什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.68,0:21:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 难得你这么担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我不太擅长记别人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 你…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为… 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你冷不丁地想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从这天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所有关于我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.57,0:23:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朋友和朋友。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
